{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"1be6814a-e64b-4008-acf4-5db82994eded","content":"Your project uses **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** (MTP) with MSTest 3.8. To enable hang detection, you need the `HangDump` extension package.","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_a0wyJsYYRLuywi2j9IPZch","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Adding hang dump support"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_rIu4Ute0cYv85eRXbydVyr","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/sv-f682d36057024f738bdb02fa7bc44040 && dotnet add package Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.HangDump 2>&1 | tail -5","description":"Add HangDump extension package","initial_wait":30},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"Add HangDump extension package"}],"interactionId":"db79bb53-c23f-4ef8-aab5-07f3ec210e47","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"This is using Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) as the test runner, with MSTest 3.8.0. The user wants a 5-minute hang timeout.\n\nFor Microsoft.Testing.Platform, there's a `--hangdump` option or `--hang-dump` that can detect hanging tests. The hang timeout can be set via `--hangdump-timeout` or similar.\n\nLet me check the exact CLI flag. With MTP, the command would be:\n\n```\ndotnet test -- --hangdump --hangdump-timeout 5m\n```\n\nOr it might be:\n```\ndotnet test --hang-dump --hang-dump-timeout 5m\n\n\n```\n\nActually, since this is using Microsoft.Testing.Platform (as indicated by the global.json `test.runner` setting), the test executable supports `--hang-dump` and `--hang-dump-timeout` options natively. For `dotnet test` with MTP, you pass platform options after `--`. The hang dump feature requires the `Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.HangDump` package though, so I need to check if MSTest 3.8.0 bundles it or if it needs to be added separately.\n\nIn MSTest 3.x, the hang dump extension is a separate package that needs to be installed, then the user can run with the appropriate flags to capture diagnostics when tests hang.\n\n```","outputTokens":611},"id":"ded742f3-ae8f-44ca-a3f3-d9803599dced","timestamp":"2026-04-05T01:16:41.871Z","parentId":"07b6abd8-7929-4c62-9371-bd69e8e2ee00"}
